The paper deals with the problem of parallel query processing, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of distributed computing. The paper also discusses lower bounds and algorithms for communication complexity, which are topics that are commonly studied in the subfield of theoretical computer science. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DB (Databases), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), and cs.Distributed Systems.
